    <bioghist id="aspace_d63623fddba1adb4a844eba26dd4696e">
      <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
      <p>Professor Leonard Shaw joined the faculty at Polytechnic University in 1960, where he taught Electrical Engineering (EE) for 43 years.  During that time, Shaw also served as the Head of the Department of Electrical Engineering and Computer Science from 1982- 1990, and then Dean of the School of EE and CS until 1994.</p>
    </bioghist>
